{"tid":2047432,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"南韓新增38宗確診病例 37宗來自首都圈","createTime":"2020-06-02T05:55:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-02T05:55:59.000Z","uid":166360,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"41aa5aefe6fa2c70df92d468a013b858eae74354","tid":2047432,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T05:55:59.000Z","msg":"南韓新增38宗確診病例 37宗來自首都圈 <br />\n2020-06-02 HKT 13:26<br />\n<br />\n南韓新增38宗新型肺炎確診病例，除了1宗在入境檢疫過程中確診外，其他都是社區感染，全部來自首都圈，京畿道、首爾市和仁川市分別有15、14和8宗，全國累計11541人確診。<br />\n<br />\n與首爾梨泰院夜店和富川物流中心相關的病例減少，但首都圈地區教會出現群聚性感染，新增確診數字未見明顯回落。仁川富平區一名教會牧師星期日確診後，近日連續出現相關病例。<br />\n<br />\n當地同日新增1宗死亡個案，累計272人不治。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1529736-20200602.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1529736-20200602.htm&d=Lcx8qPwugtyypLbLLwesbfY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=3bc43007\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1529736-20200602.htm&h=4802dc23\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1529736-20200602.htm</a>"}]}